{"tid":1411194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"即時應對林奠黑警每日記者會 有請民間記者會","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T03:20:06.000Z","uid":220864,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17add64630a850be8a1367ca0cd8909971423056","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"黑警嘅記者會明顯係諗住帶風向<br />\n單方面攻擊示威者<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以示弱<br />\n早前有巴打提及過民間記者會<br />\n但係我一直都無follow進程<br />\n有無人可以update下定已經不了了知<br />\n<br />\n但係而家我認為係一個好好嘅方法去應對<br />\n好似搞隔空辯論同反擊咁<br />\n攞哂黑警嘅柒事濫權出嚟<br />\n例如尋日打穿平民個頭<br />\n拖女義士入天水圍<br />\n港島亂射催淚彈等<br />\n好似強迫tvb播tvb不告訴你的事咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢地想單方面帶風向<br />\n我地就要反擊<br />\n每日用番相同嘅方式去攻擊番班黑警<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"60f92a63318cd904c512915f394a417a958fc451","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:09:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"312cab1a5e0f15df43c23efa32ca99b80b8a95a3","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69d56fca487f6687717def1e136222a96f8a015e","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e82dd16510a462dce7ebb9f028f45f7bd0af93c0","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5ed2ad4ed460fe1672417aee5fa1b276dec12aa","tid":1411194,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"搞記者會呢幾樣野要留意下，就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以打反擊</span></span><br />\n即係唔可以佢記者會講咗乜，我地逐點澄清fact check<br />\n因為咁樣做都係會令佢地嘅agenda得到曝光同討論度<br />\n<br />\n對付fake news一個好方法就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直接攻擊源頭</span></strong><br />\n同大家講，呢篇新聞嘅源頭不可信，所以呢篇野係fake news<br />\n同理，我地都要話俾所有人知，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府個記者會不可信</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n同時統一搞記者會，就<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有成為大台嘅潛在風險</strong></span><br />\n要仔細諗清楚"},{"pid":"e6f24a82663b4e8bae1e811d55fcb09b0164d59f","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a95266b5b14a80bc8388ec17b1067218489dfea","tid":1411194,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:10:55.000Z","msg":"hocc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd8596f2e5bda7b5ca468598533f56d9212eaa7","tid":1411194,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"應該成立連登新聞關注組，請記者幫手向官員提問下連登各手足問題。"},{"pid":"0e3a47cdff8881a993fe5eef6a7eceb58f9462fe","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"另外可以邀請埋受害人例如陳生老豆<br />\n或者連登女義士<br />\n上去講述被襲經過"},{"pid":"e9ac4f6168e7b4bf1092d69b1c5d467d6ab7fa92","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a08517137535066ca97d9750dc5eab17933a7221","tid":1411194,"uid":149008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"支持!"},{"pid":"2f2661aa3335d5a713a5c51bd3a6a25d72f438f9","tid":1411194,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"請統一口徑！！！<br />\n唔好用偏激、嘩眾取寵既做法<br />\n一定要客觀而且清晰列出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非禮及意圖強姦<br />\n高處暗位開鎗暗殺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n用字好重要，否則只會令人覺得你只係洩憤同作大<br />\n請準確地列出所犯罪行<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位文宣手足！！"},{"pid":"9e563a93c07d0dc751a26e6dcece5940283b2b58","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e09912933e87e1383eb5535d7db0c78296408508","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63b1ed3e1f3ee391f075a87882bdc71b19fab660","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f18133dd90e58577cbb77c936326c87c499dc38","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4b8a2dce6a3a23d92139cb88985fa80b20d13b3","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6798469a59231bdd32c86a24969b1179f61c45b1","tid":1411194,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}